    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――LizNoir、新年初のライブバトル当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――LizNoir's first live battle in this year",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "……うん、良かった\nお客さん、沢山入ってるわね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yeah‚ that's good.\nThere are a lot of people in the audience…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたんですか？　本番はまだ先ですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What's wrong? The performance is still a while away.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "お客さんの入りが、気になって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm concerned about the turnout…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "チケット、即完売したって教えたじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I told you the tickets sold out immediately‚ didn't I?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "そうだけど……実感したかったのよ。自分の目で見てね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's true‚ but… I wanted to feel it for myself. See it with my own eyes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "今日の相手は、莉央さん達の古巣……\nバンプロが売り出し中の若手強豪グループです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today's opponent is LizNoir's former company…\nThey're an up-and-coming powerhouse currently being promoted by Van Pro.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "そうね、私も知っている子達よ\nライブ映像を観たけれど……上手になってた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I know them too.\nI watched their live footage… They've gotten better.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "これからもっと伸びるわね\n強いわよ、彼女達",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They're going to grow even more from now on.\nThey're strong‚ those girls.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……勝てそうですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Do you think we can win?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "負ける気はしないわ\n……私、油断してるように見える？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't feel like losing.\n…Do I seem complacent?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、そういう感じはしないです\nなんて言うか……いい意味で力が抜けてるというか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I don't get that feeling.\nIt's more like… you're relaxed in a good way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "私は、メンバーと自分の実力をよく知っているわ\nファンにはそれを素直に観て、楽しんでもらえればいい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know the abilities of the members and myself well.\nI want the fans to see that and enjoy it sincerely.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 68.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "そうすれば、結果は自然とついてくる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If we do that‚ the results will naturally follow.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "今日のLizNoirのステージ、楽しみにしています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm looking forward to today's LizNoir stage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "任せてちょうだい。圧倒的なパフォーマンスでファンを\n……いえ、ライバルさえ魅了して、完璧に勝つ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Leave it to me. We'll overwhelm the fans with an overwhelming performance…\n…No‚ we'll captivate even our rivals and win perfectly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "そうして、近いうちにアイドルの頂点に立つわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And then‚ we'll soon stand at the pinnacle of idols.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "……やっぱり、莉央さんは以前と変わりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You've really changed‚ Rio-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "そう？　言ってることは同じだと思うけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that so? I think I'm saying the same things as before‚ though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、だけど以前は「勝つ」と強気に叫んでいた\n今は静かで……でも力強さを感じます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ but before‚ you used to shout \"victory\" with confidence.\nNow you're calm… but I can still feel your strength.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "……大物感が出てきたんじゃないですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You're starting to feel like a big deal‚ aren't you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "からかうのはやめてちょうだい\nそんな年齢じゃないんだから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please stop teasing me.\nI'm not that young‚ you know…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "それでなくても、こころに毎日\n莉央さんはお疲れでしょう～お肩をお揉みしますよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ Kokoro is like…\n\"Rio-san must be tired~ Let me massage your shoulders~\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 121.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "――って、からかわれてるんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I'm being teased everyday.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "からかうフリをして莉央さんと仲良くしたいだけですよ\nこころと愛は、莉央さんと葵を慕ってますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She just want to be good friends with you‚ using teasing as an excuse.\nKokoro and Ai admire Rio-san and Aoi‚ you know.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 131.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "そうね。最近は、あの子達のおふざけも\n可愛く感じられるようになってきたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. Recently‚ I've started to find their antics…\n…adorable.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 137.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、最初はあの子達と組むの\n嫌でしょうがなかったのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha‚ at first‚ I really didn't like\nbeing teamed up with them…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 146.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03-rio017.m4a",
      "text": "海外修行があって、バンプロを離れて\n……そして星見プロに来て、私も変わったのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After the overseas training‚ leaving Van Pro behind…\n…and then coming to Hoshimi Pro‚ I've changed too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 152.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03-rio018.m4a",
      "text": "でも、変わらないこともある\n私がLizNoirのセンターであり続けること",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But there are things that haven't changed.\nI will continue to be LizNoir's center.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03-rio019.m4a",
      "text": "それは、こころにも愛にも……葵にだって、譲れないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's something I won't give up on‚ not even for Kokoro and Ai… or Aoi.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 163.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。これからもLizNoirを\n引っ張っていって下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. Please continue\nto lead LizNoir.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんがセンターに立つLizNoirは\n凄く輝きます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "LizNoir shines brilliantly\nwhen Rio-san is at the center.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 173.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03-rio020.m4a",
      "text": "……ありがとう、嬉しいわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Thank you‚ that makes me happy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 175.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03-rio021.m4a",
      "text": "今日、勝てたら、またあのお店で一緒に\n祝杯をあげてくれる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If we win today‚\nlet's have a toast together at that place again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 178.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 180.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんです……けど、ほどほどでお願いします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course…But not too much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03-rio022.m4a",
      "text": "約束よ。じゃあ、そろそろ行ってくるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Promise. Well then‚ I'll be going soon.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.7666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5600.000000000023,
          "startTime": 191.3666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "……LizNoirが圧倒的大差で勝利、か\nさすがだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…LizNoir winning by a large margin‚ huh?\nAs expected.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 197.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03-rio023.m4a",
      "text": "みなさん、本日は私達のステージを\n観に来てくれてありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone‚ thank you for\ncoming to see our stage today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 202.4,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2066.6666667000018,
          "startTime": 204.4666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03-rio024.m4a",
      "text": "今まで、私達にはいろんな出来事がありました……\nこのステージに立っているのも、奇跡のようなことです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We've experienced various things up until now…\nJust being on this stage is like a miracle.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 210.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03-rio025.m4a",
      "text": "でも、それは奇跡ではなく、もっと凄いもの……\n努力、そして何よりみなさんの応援が起こした必然です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it's not a miracle‚ it's something even more amazing…\nIt's the result of our efforts and‚ most importantly‚ your support.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 219.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03-rio026.m4a",
      "text": "だから――みなさん、応援ありがとうございます\nそしてこれからも、応援をよろしくお願いします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So… everyone‚ thank you for your support.\nAnd please continue to support us from now on.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 229.7666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2666.6666666000083,
          "startTime": 232.4333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03-rio027.m4a",
      "text": "私達LizNoirは、奇跡を超える――\n奇跡よりずっと凄い必然を、成し遂げてみせます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We‚ LizNoir‚ will achieve something even more amazing…\n…something that goes beyond miracles.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 237.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03-rio028.m4a",
      "text": "……あっ、それとごめんなさい\nみなさんに大切なことを伝え忘れていました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ah‚ I'm sorry.\nI forgot to tell you something important.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 244.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_03-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "大切なこと？　今日はそんな発表の予定はないはず――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Something important? There shouldn't be any announcements today…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 248.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
